preview.text: Thanks to everyone who came to our fundraiser and those who attended the book discussion this week. This week's events were a great way to cap off the semester for Maryland Science Café! Congratulations to Ryan, Luke, and Hita for being elected as our new board members! Based on the poll results, our plan for next semester is to meet on Mondays instead of Thursdays (still every other week at 7:30 PM). Stay tuned for more details about the club in the Terplink and GroupMe when we enter the spring semester. Have a great weekend!
